{"tid":2217470,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"(活動）我每星期都會喺連登揀篇故，與在囚/還押手足","createTime":"2020-09-25T12:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T08:00:39.000Z","uid":134474,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6f92467a5fc4811538f63c29b39a0b249ac337fe","tid":2217470,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"大家有冇諗過想同身在囹圄手足分享故事，假如自己唔知應該寫乜俾手足，但又想為手足解悶，何不嘗喺連登揀篇認為合適故，寄俾手足？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先向原作者表明目的並取得同意，之後Print或手寫方式<br />\n<br />\n並作出適當分段（因為寄俾手足信紙數目有限，唔建議一次出哂成篇）<br />\n<br />\n選擇合適題材，預咗被柳記Check，可以嘅話check下有冇啲唔適合地方，自行河蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議對象最好固定（手足都想追故），並鼓勵佢哋同其他手足分享故事<br />\n<br />\n重甜或逃獄就不了（雖然我係勁想share甜故<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）但預咗bam"},{"pid":"e1cc142bb8a69cea8800c430933a0264f07c0c06","tid":2217470,"uid":134474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"各位追故巴絲，如果你追緊故，但又想同手足分享，歡迎做分享師"},{"pid":"e44b2e7522dc11404f85a21e1d9d23e9ef3b49d3","tid":2217470,"uid":308531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0f35e08484a01d200431b462f28046925de8730","tid":2217470,"uid":2099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"GOOD IDEA.<br />\n推"},{"pid":"3726ce1e920a84f847f8a149e92332059647cffa","tid":2217470,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0f35e08484a01d200431b462f28046925de8730","tid":2217470,"uid":2099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"GOOD IDEA.<br />\n推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:50:01.000Z","msg":"多謝你"},{"pid":"7876797680ee102bcbffd2e45f3f88a25a549af4","tid":2217470,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:50:44.000Z","msg":"分享愛"},{"pid":"bcbca55d380cae06f9000